Package de.rwth.idsg.adapter.soap2json

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ResponseObjectCreator
    This class is responsible of syntactically converting SOAP response messages into JSON-RPC response messages.
    ResponseProcessor
    The main class that handles Camel exchanges to initiate and manage the mapping process of responses.
    SoapFaultProcessor
    This class handles a SOAP fault and sends a JSON-RPC error response to client.
